title: SkillSwap
description: SkillSwap is a platform that allows users to exchange their skills with others. Users can create a profile, list their skills, and find other users to exchange skills with.

title: Resume Builder
description: This is an app that allows users to create a resume by filling out a form. The app will then generate a resume based on the information provided.

title: Interview Experience
description: This is a website where users can share their interview experiences. Users can read and search for interview experiences by company, role, or location.
